{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534502844&di=59d464db9532ba77cbfc5da3b6c58780&src=http%3A%2F%2Fc.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F72f082025aafa40f011a64f1a364034f78f01939.jpg","summary":"湖北经济学院(Hubei University of Economics)位于湖北省省会武汉市，是以经济学、管理学为主干，法学、文学、理学、工学、艺术学协调发展的一所省属全日制公办普通本科高校。学校的前身可追溯到创办于1907年的湖北商业中学堂及其后的另外两所学校发展而来，至今已有百余年办学历史。2002年9月经国家教育部批准，在原湖北商业高等专科学校、武汉金融高等专科学校、湖北省计划管理干部学院的基础上合并组建为湖北经济学院。2016年入选中西部高校基础能力建设工程。截至2016年8月31日，该校占地面积1740亩，校舍建筑面积62万平方米。设有19个教学单位，有硕士专业学位授权点1个，开办本科专业56个。有专任教师752人，全日制研究生、本科在校学生1.6万人。","tags":["财经类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"2002","所在地区":"武汉市江夏藏龙岛科技园区杨桥湖大道","院校隶属":"湖北省","硕士点":"1"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502844&di=85fe6548ab9b4ab744a0435602aa88b3&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3676195040%2C787567022%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502844&di=6f4ccef3c4e22d21485489db0c2bd4b9&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3700919036%2C972568850%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502844&di=560163ddad2f351909391ac53b3d9336&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3562416638%2C809838149%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502844&di=cc81b4a358252fea188f27c9201fb86d&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3569566702%2C3945542732%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502844&di=261777c2162bccebc5e6dc1b7b3070be&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3746652535%2C937203975%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA